Easiest scraping/data extraction tool on the market that is FREE.

* Smart Select - Click on something on website, get all the items that look similar.
* Configuration is saved for each webpage. 
* Select any attribute of the element to extract.
* Supports several pagination and custom URL navigation options (easy-to-use).
